dcterms:description: 2D T2 FLAIR FSE brain MRI k-space data acquired from a 3T GE Signa Premier scanner, consisting of 553 training, 197 validation, and 100 test 2D slices from 31 subjects, used as motion-artifact-free ground truth.
dcterms:title: 2D T2 FLAIR FSE brain MRI k-space data

dcterms:description: A collection of motion-free k-space data used to simulate motion-corrupted data for training and testing the motion correction network.
dcterms:title: Motion-free k-space data

dcterms:description: Acquired k-space measurements from two scans of the same subject in different head positions, used to create realistic test examples for the motion correction method.
dcterms:title: Acquired k-space measurements (yi,1 and yi,2)
